00:42:10.020 --> 00:42:12.700
And then do you have anything
that you can reveal, as far as

00:42:12.700 --> 00:42:15.400
plans beyond that
or what's next?

00:42:15.400 --> 00:42:17.970
PETER GABRIEL: Well, there still
is this quite a lot of

00:42:17.970 --> 00:42:22.630
