there are a few projects that

00:42:22.630 --> 00:42:26.740
I think I'll get back to
work in September.

00:42:26.740 --> 00:42:31.710
So I guess we'll
know more then.

00:42:31.710 --> 00:42:34.220
We're trying to get--

00:42:34.220 --> 00:42:36.650
there's a thing called
Gabble, which is

00:42:36.650 --> 00:42:37.930
