00:42:37.930 --> 00:42:40.760
we're trying to do a visual
language for the net where it

00:42:40.760 --> 00:42:42.990
turns words into pictures.

00:42:42.990 --> 00:42:49.445
And we're just starting
with that.

00:42:49.445 --> 00:42:51.780
And I'm sure I'll be hustling
for help later

00:42:51.780 --> 00:42:54.660
on, so don't worry.

00:42:54.660 --> 00:42:55.670
INTERVIEWER: Have a wonderful
show tonight.

00:42:55.670 --> 00:42:57.810
Have a great rest of the tour
and a great sabbatical.

00:42:57.810 --> 00:42:59.760
